research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Bowie, TX operates under a council/manager form of government. The Mayor and six City Council members are elected at large. Council members are also associated with specific precincts (North Pct. 1, South Pct. 2, East Pct. 3) for administrative purposes. Mayor Gaylynn Burris won her final term in November 2025. Brandon Walker, Laramie Truax, and Laura Sproles were sworn in as new council members in November 2024.
